data.description: Tastefully REMODELED POOL HOME in the HEART OF VALRICO! 1.19 acres of fully fenced and cleared space!!   Bring your RV/ boats and campers.  NO HOA!!!!  4 Bedroom 2 Bath and oversized 2 Car Garage/ Workshop. This Freshly Painted home features an open floor-plan, large kitchen with Dining Room. The remodeled kitchen overlooks the family and dinning room and features all wood cabinets, brand new granite countertops and updated appliance package! New Custom Ceramic tile, luxurious laminate and new carpet thru out the entire home! Spacious master bedroom and a nice large walk-in closet.  Fully screened massive inground pool with new pumps and equipment  New AC in 2021. Hurry, this will not last long!!!!!!! The open floor plan makes this home perfect for entertaining. Close to local parks/ schools and everything the greater Tampa Bay offers.
